# Target Site: your-site.com

## What it is
Your Product is a community SEO app that surfaces ranking issues, decay, indexing problems, and content opportunities. Live at https://www.your-site.com. Stack: Cloudflare Workers + D1.

## Audience
SEO practitioners, agency owners, and in-house marketers who want to use AI to rank faster in 2026. They have tried generic advice and want what actually moves rankings: AI Overviews, fan-out, programmatic SEO, content refreshing, automation with Claude Code.

## Voice
- Direct, concrete, practical. No fluff, no hype, no emojis.
- Never use em dashes. Use colons, commas, parentheses, or separate sentences.
- Senior operator talking to other operators.
- Short sentences. Specific numbers. Real examples over generic claims.

## Topics in scope
- AI Overviews and how to rank in them
- Query fan-out and AI search engines (ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Mode)
- Content decay, refresh, and reindexing
- GSC monitoring and alerts
- Programmatic SEO with Claude Code
- Three Kings (title tag, H1, first paragraph)
- Pillar and cluster content models
- Internal linking automation
- Schema markup for AI search

## Topics out of scope
- Generic "what is SEO" beginner content
- Black hat tactics
- PPC, paid social, branding tutorials
- Keywords unrelated to AI/SEO automation

## Existing wins to reference (do not fabricate)
- your-site.com ranks position #6.54 for "query fan out ai search"
- example-real-estate.com Spanish post on the 8000 UF property tax exemption: 1,442 impressions, position #7 in 3 months, written by Claude

